        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You are the third generation of an Italian famliy. Your great grandparents on both sides came over on a slow boat from the Boot of Europe. Then they married out of the neighberhood and now you only have a real connection on your fathers side that was from the old country. Your mother was a wasp from the Bronx that fell head over heels for your father, but she loved the Italian culture and brought you up with it all. Later on, you fell in with the punky computer nerds and in no time you became a hacker of the first order. That is how you came to the notice of your sire and the clan. You loved learning the Technomancy was a thing but you’ve always had a problem with the clan structure. The way that your chantry was run left you feeling just a little looked down on. The fact that you were one of the best technomancers in your chantry made you feel like you deserved more respect, or at least a higher ranking within the clan. The idea of anarchy always appealed to you, but you are definitely a faithful and loyal member of the Camarilla. You heard rumors of Lady Carna wanting to shake things up a bit. You are definitely looking forward to more rumors coming out of Europe in that regard. until then you spend your nights simply being the best. You have a heavy reliance on magic, because why not, you were a great hacker before, now you will a one kindred Anon."
        ],
