          "staff_generated_concept": "You absolutely do know that there are Tremere Anarchs, and many of them are technomancers. You've even worked with some on the downlow, including a well-known one, Mariska St. John. You've never met her or any of them in real life, I mean, your Regent is always watching, but there are those in court who hang with the Anarchs and talk to them. Maybe they can hook you up."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "You've been hearing chatter of some strange occurences going on in the web, some weird and dangerous stuff. You know there is such a thing as human technomages too, powerful ones, ones that make you look like a snot-nosed kid. You know that the Tremere have always warned you against them, and you don't disagree, but you may be one of the few people who really understands what it is they are doing and how dangerous it is for everyone else."
        },
        {
          "staff_generated_concept": "Player Amended History",
          "column_3": "Date Submited"
        }
      ]
    },
